description: Frontend coding standards — React, TypeScript, TailwindCSS, components
globs: src/**/*.tsx

## Frontend Rules
1. TypeScript strict mode, no `any`
2. TailwindCSS v4 for all styling
3. Every page: loading skeleton, empty state, error state, success state
4. Framer Motion for animations (fade + slide up pattern)
5. Lucide React for icons
6. No emojis in any UI text
7. Zustand selectors for minimum re-renders
8. useCallback for stable callbacks, useRef for mutable values
9. Components: PascalCase, one per file, typed props interface
10. Event handlers: handle{EventName}
11. Imports order: external → internal, absolute → relative
